{
  "stem": "22889.4",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know, once in a while, somebody got-- because we didn't have no-- the Ukrainian watch us.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That's-- their own Gestapo used to come around, and they had their own police, werkschutz.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There were pretty nice to us.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "There were a couple of them, that wasn't so bad.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Was a small, very small camp.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "There were 60 of us was, that's all.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But when we came to Plaszow, was a different story.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "There were some people already there-- not too many.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We start to build the barracks.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And we built the barracks.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Then they bring the people from the ghetto, they liquidated ghetto in Krakow.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "They brought them to Plaszow.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And this commander Goeth, he was unbelievable.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "He was tall man, handsome man-- good-looking man.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Always used to ride on a white horse, and his girlfriend, again, on a black horse.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "She always wore white turtleneck.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I never forget.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "She was good-looking woman.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "I don't know if she was German or she was Polish-- I don't know who she was, really.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "But every time he was riding, we had to stand up-- whatever you did, you'd stand up.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And they called, [NON-ENGLISH], and bow down to him, and report to him.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "If he didn't like something, he'd stop by and many times I've seen he took the pistol and kill people for no reason, just like that.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "This was his satisfaction.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "Friend of mine, lives in Israel, his name is Jacob Schneider-- he still lives, I just saw him a few months ago.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "He used to work for him in his home-- he used to take care of his dogs.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "He took care of his dogs.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So he used to feed them the best kind of meat.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "After work, he used to come to our barracks.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
